    <text type="letter">
        <body>
            <pb xml:id="leaf001r" facs="loc_jc.00428_large.jpg" type="recto"/>
            <opener>
                <dateline rend="right">
                    <name type="place">Camden</name>
                    <date when="1890-06-19">June 19 1890</date>
                </dateline>
                <salute>My dear friend &amp; all</salute>
            </opener>
            <p>It is a wonderful fine day, cool enough &amp; I am feeling fairly&#8212;every thing going right (but of 
                course steadily down hill)&#8212;Young George<ptr target="loc.03880_n3"/> was here, &amp; I was glad to see him&#8212;he looks 
                well&#8212;I hear from Dr Bucke<ptr target="n0119"/> f'm Canada, &amp; f'm 
                Edw'd Carpenter<ptr target="n0141b"/>&#8212;he is well&#8212;my friends the Smiths<ptr target="n4979b"/> 
                (of Germantown) are all settled in London &amp; seem to like it&#8212;Herbert<ptr target="n0262"/> is 
                still at Centreport Long Island<ptr target="loc.03881_n1b"/>&#8212;I get splendid letters f'm Col. Ingersoll<ptr target="n0839"/> 
                &amp; a noble book of his later pieces (I wish dear Harry<ptr target="n0590"/> could see them 
                all&#8212;he would gloat over them)&#8212;I get out in wheel chair<ptr target="loc.03012_n1"/>&#8212;am quite helpless &amp; if I 
                live much longer shall be blind&#8212;Love to you &amp; George<ptr target="n0852c"/> &amp; Ed<ptr target="n0589c"/> 
                &amp; Deb<ptr target="n0844c"/> &amp; all&#8212;this card is the dinner card<ptr target="loc.03880_n4"/> for curiosity&#8212;</p>
            <closer>
                <signed>Walt Whitman</signed>
            </closer>
            <postscript>
                <p><date when="1890-06-20">June 20</date></p>
                <p>Another fine bright day&#8212;all ab't as usual&#8212;all well &amp; quiet&#8212;best love 
                    &amp; wishes to you all&#8212;</p>  
            </postscript>
        </body>
